</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="idaaecc339-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 1980 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Amendment by <ref href="/us/pl/96/513">Pub. L. 96–513</ref> effective <date date="1981-09-15">Sept. 15, 1981</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/96/513/s701">section 701 of Pub. L. 96–513</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s101">section 101 of this title</ref>.</p>
